name: ETC Premium
description: Introducing Ethereum Plus (ETH⁺) — it's like regular Ethereum, but with a gym membership and a better skincare routine. ETH⁺ isn’t just a coin — it’s a glow-up. Powered by pure smart contract swagger and caffeinated with multichain ambition, this token comes with all the decentralized goodness you love, plus a little extra sauce. Think of it as Ethereum’s overachieving sibling — the one who shows up to family dinners with passive income, gas fee discounts, and a DAO invite for your dog.
